{"sections":[],"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/SQ"],"type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"A resolved document is a fully dereferenced","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"OpenAPI document that has been further distilled","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to canonical representations of each component. You","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"create a ","type":"text"},{"code":"ResolvedDocument","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" by calling the ","type":"text"},{"code":"resolved()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"method on a ","type":"text"},{"code":"DereferencedDocument","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@dynamicMemberLookup"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"ResolvedDocument"}],"platforms":["Linux"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Overview","anchor":"overview","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"OpenAPI documents have two distinct forms of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"distributing information such that not all relevant","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"bits of information are available in one structural","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"part of an OpenAPI Document.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"orderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Documents can contain references. This is great"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"because authors can make one part of an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"OpenAPI document more concise by referencing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a component instead of writing it inline and it also"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"allows shared definitions to be re-used throughout"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the document."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Documents can define and override certain things at"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"different levels of their structure. For example, a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"document may define a shared set of Security"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Requirements at the root and then override those"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Security Requirements for particular Operations."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Both of these features of OpenAPI documents make it"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"impossible to answer certain questions about a particular"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"route or endpoint without looking to multiple disparate parts"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of the document and then applying certain rules to determine"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the relevant semantic definition of the route or endpoint being"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"studied."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"OpenAPIKit defines canonical forms (i.e. the only true definitions)","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of endpoints, routes, and the whole document. These types (named","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"ResolvedEndpoint","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"ResolvedRoute","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", and ","type":"text"},{"code":"ResolvedDocument","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":")","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"each allow you to get complete information about the respective components","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"without looking to other parts of the document.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Example"}],"type":"strong"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You want to know what all of the parameters for a particular "},{"code":"PATCH","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" endpoint are."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Without the "},{"code":"ResolvedEndpoint","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" type, you would need to look at the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"OpenAPI.Operation","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" representing the endpoint, the "},{"code":"OpenAPI.PathItem","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"representing the route containing the endpoint, and you would need to potentially"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"resolve references to the "},{"code":"OpenAPI.Components","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"With "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ResolvedDocument"},{"type":"text","text":", the same task is much simpler:"}]},{"code":["let document: OpenAPI.Document = ...","","let resolvedDocument = try document","    .locallyDereferenced()","    .resolved()","","let endpoint = resolvedDocument","    .routesByPath[\"\/example\/path\"]!.patch!","","\/\/ This will be all parameters defined anywhere that","\/\/ apply to this endpoint:","let parameters = endpoint.parameters"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":null}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit\/ResolvedDocument"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","externalID":"s:10OpenAPIKit16ResolvedDocumentV","symbolKind":"struct","roleHeading":"Structure","title":"ResolvedDocument","